ak in the differential scanning calorimetry\ncurves, about 50%~70% volume reduction for the Ti2Ni phase, and approximately\n35 HV reduction on microhardness.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Feb 2022 20:50:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-22"}
